The collector that owns this NFT will be able to talk to cats.


During my study I discovered that contrary to popular belief felines are extremely smart. What sounds like a simple meow is actually many big words put together. Cats are always willing to make deals for tasty kitty treats. So if you need a cat to spy on someone that you suspect is being unfaithful, all it will cost you is a bowl of milk and some salmon.


Please direct message me after purchase.
